'''苏丹'''（Sudan，{{bd|1973年||2018年|3月19日|catIdx=Sudan}}）是一頭雄性[[北白犀|北白犀]]，它原先生活在非洲，1975年被人工捕獲，同年被帶到[[捷克|捷克]]的{{link-en|拉貝河畔皇宮野生動物園|Safari Park Dvůr Králové}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mládě milénia: Cesta k úspěchu|url=http://www.rozhlas.cz/priroda/porady/_zprava/6225|accessdate=2018-06-06|date=2000-04-11|publisher=Czech Radio|archive-date=2018-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180324082813/http://www.rozhlas.cz/priroda/porady/_zprava/6225|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在該動物園一直呆到2009年。此後蘇丹又來到[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]][[萊基皮亞郡|萊基皮亞郡]]的{{link-en|奥尔佩耶塔保护区|Ol Pejeta Conservancy}}，並在那裡度過餘生<ref name="Khomami1">{{Cite news|author=Khomami|first=Nadia|title=Death of white rhino in Kenya leaves only six animals alive in the world|url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2014/oct/18/northern-white-rhino-dies-six-alive-world|accessdate=2014-12-07|publisher=The Guardian|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209092742/http://www.theguardian.com/environment/2014/oct/18/northern-white-rhino-dies-six-alive-world|archivedate=2014-12-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在蘇丹去世前夕，它是世界上仅有的三头在世的[[北白犀|北白犀]]之一，也是最后一头已知的雄性[[北白犀|北白犀]]。苏丹因患有并发症，于2018年3月19日被實施[[安乐死|安乐死]]<ref name="NPR">Eyder Peralta (2018) [https://www.npr.org/sections/parallels/2018/03/20/591075801/sudan-worlds-last-male-northern-white-rhino-dies "Sudan, World's Last Male Northern White Rhino, Dies"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/parallels/2018/03/20/591075801/sudan-worlds-last-male-northern-white-rhino-dies |date=20180320143156 }} ''NPR'', 20 March 2018. Accessed 20 March 2018.</ref>。

